description:
Sam Altman and Ilya Sutskever at Tel Aviv University.
Main takeaway: You have to have faith. Very inspiring 🙌

Q: What makes OpenAI the leader, and how do you keep at it?
Sam: Focus, conviction, and talent density. Culture of repeatable innovation.
Ilya: Progress in AI is a game of faith. If you have the most faith, you will make the most progress. You have to believe.

Sam and Ilya also spokes about super-intelligence risks, potential, how far ahead GPT4 is from open-source models, and how the next model will make GPT4 look basic. 

Sam also shared that on his ChatGPT you will mostly see educational use - "Teach me about X asap."
title: Sam Altman and Ilya Sutskever - Talk at Tel Aviv - June-5-2023
